Add Firebase-based Google login and cloud sync (optional)

- New firebase-config.js (placeholder until user fills it in)
- New cloud-sync.js ES module: auth, Firestore with offline persistence,
  real-time plan + checklist sync, multi-plan, email-based sharing
- index.html gets a Google Sign-in bar, plan switcher, New/Rename/Delete,
  Share modal, and integrates with existing saveState/saveDone paths
- firestore.rules enforces per-user membership via memberEmails
- FIREBASE_SETUP.md walks through a 10-minute one-time Firebase setup
- When Firebase isn't configured, the app behaves exactly as before
  (pure localStorage, no network, no UI changes)
